NETHERLANDS COASTGUARD
NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 38 310316 UTC JAN
WARNING SEASTATE
WAVE HEIGHT WARNING 300CM TSS TERSCHELLING - GERMAN BIGHT
ISSUED AT 310300UTC JAN
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M ARE AT RISK
OF LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS IN
PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO NORTHERLY
DIRECTION. THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER COURSE IF
NECESSARY TO AVOID COMING ABEAM TO THE WAVES AND
TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE MEASURES TO AVOID LOSING
CONTAINERS.
